# Drag and Drop Integration

## Objective
Enable users to drag quest cards between columns to change their status.

## Tasks
1. Integrate a drag-and-drop library compatible with SvelteKit or use standard HTML5 DnD API.
2. Make quest cards draggable.
3. Make columns drop zones.
4. Capture the `onDrop` event with the quest ID and new status.
